{"tid":17822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國王儲哇集拉隆功正式繼位　成新王「拉瑪十世」","createTime":"2016-12-02T03:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T03:30:07.000Z","uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f8d67dde64e1bd6a81cada24a864a1fe444a89b","tid":17822,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】泰國新國王哇集拉隆功正式繼位！泰國政府晚上宣布，王儲哇集拉隆功正式接受國會的繼位邀請，成為泰國新國王。<br />\n　　不過新國王的登基加冕儀式會待普密蓬的一年喪期結束後才舉行，哇集拉隆功預料會立即簽署一項由軍政府起草的新憲法，將軍方掌握的政治權力制度化，穩固與軍隊的良好關係，成為他的重要籌碼。<br />\n　　現年64歲的哇集拉隆功在20歲時已被確立為儲君，是曼谷王朝的第10位君主－「拉瑪十世」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%8E%8B%E5%84%B2%E5%93%87%E9%9B%86%E6%8B%89%E9%9A%86%E5%8A%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%B9%BC%E4%BD%8D-%E6%88%90%E6%96%B0%E7%8E%8B-%E6%8B%89%E7%91%AA%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%96-142500884.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2584%25B2%25E5%2593%2587%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%258B%2589%25E9%259A%2586%25E5%258A%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%258E%258B-%25E6%258B%2589%25E7%2591%25AA%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25B8%2596-142500884.html&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=47939310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%8E%8B%E5%84%B2%E5%93%87%E9%9B%86%E6%8B%89%E9%9A%86%E5%8A%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%B9%BC%E4%BD%8D-%E6%88%90%E6%96%B0%E7%8E%8B-%E6%8B%89%E7%91%AA%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%96-142500884.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}